r stage, can be found in the menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429530/extras/e274b5b69d39792571df5aa4b85f406b.webp?t=1773174690\" width=618 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429530/extras/97606becab95cc963b9b94e88e73b31e.poster.avif?t=1773174690\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429530/extras/97606becab95cc963b9b94e88e73b31e.webm?t=1773174690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429530/extras/97606becab95cc963b9b94e88e73b31e.mp4?t=1773174690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forge gives you the possibility of merging your hard-earned upgrades, to achieve bigger and better bonuses. Combine a multitude of possible items and find the best possible upgrade path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combining your upgrades always results in a better bonus. Combine multiple of the same, to decided the result type.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Range</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reload Time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cost Reduction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armor Damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shield Damage</p></li></ul>",
